---
title: BeaconLink Policy Evaluation Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as Platform Operator
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Identity Provider
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant PDP as Policy Decision Point
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Planner as Deployment Planner
    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Audit as Audit Service
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent

    %% =====================================================
    %% Request Submission
    %% =====================================================

    User->>API: Submit deployment request

    API->>Auth: Authenticate identity
    Auth-->>API: Identity verified

    API->>Policy: Evaluate deployment request

    Note right of Policy: Evaluation begins before<br/>any workflow execution.

    %% =====================================================
    %% Policy Context Collection
    %% =====================================================

    Policy->>Inventory: Retrieve infrastructure context

    Inventory-->>Policy: Sites, agents, labels,<br/>runtime capabilities, ownership

    Policy->>Planner: Retrieve deployment metadata

    Planner-->>Policy: Manifest, revision,<br/>deployment targets

    Policy->>Policy: Build evaluation context

    %% =====================================================
    %% Policy Evaluation
    %% =====================================================

    Policy->>PDP: Execute policy rules

    Note right of PDP: Evaluate:<br/>• RBAC permissions<br/>• Organization policies<br/>• Deployment restrictions<br/>• Runtime compatibility<br/>• Resource quotas<br/>• Compliance rules<br/>• Secret access<br/>• Network constraints

    PDP->>PDP: Evaluate all applicable rules

    %% =====================================================
    %% Decision
    %% =====================================================

    alt Policy Approved

        PDP-->>Policy: Allow

        Policy-->>API: Authorization successful

        API->>Workflow: Create deployment workflow

        Workflow-->>API: Workflow accepted

        API-->>User: Deployment accepted

        Policy->>Events: Publish PolicyApproved

    else Policy Denied

        PDP-->>Policy: Deny with violations

        Policy->>Audit: Record policy violations

        Policy->>Events: Publish PolicyDenied

        Policy-->>API: Authorization failed

        API-->>User: Deployment rejected

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Policy Verification
    %% =====================================================

    opt Runtime Enforcement

        Workflow->>Agent: Dispatch deployment

        Agent->>Policy: Re-evaluate execution policy

        Policy->>PDP: Validate runtime context

        alt Runtime Authorized

            PDP-->>Policy: Allow execution

            Policy-->>Agent: Continue deployment

        else Runtime Denied

            PDP-->>Policy: Deny execution

            Policy-->>Agent: Abort deployment

            Agent->>Events: Publish RuntimePolicyViolation

        end

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Compliance
    %% =====================================================

    loop Continuous Reconciliation

        Agent->>Policy: Validate running workload

        Policy->>Inventory: Retrieve latest policies

        Inventory-->>Policy: Updated policy state

        Policy->>PDP: Re-evaluate compliance

        alt Policy Drift Detected

            PDP-->>Policy: Non-compliant

            Policy->>Events: Publish PolicyViolationDetected

            Policy->>Audit: Record compliance failure

            Policy-->>Agent: Trigger reconciliation

        else Compliant

            PDP-->>Policy: Compliant

            Policy-->>Agent: Continue operation

        end

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Audit and Observability
    %% =====================================================

    Policy->>Audit: Record evaluation result
    Audit->>Events: Publish PolicyEvaluationCompleted

    Note over Policy,PDP: Every policy decision is<br/>deterministic, auditable,<br/>and continuously enforceable<br/>throughout the workload lifecycle.